                                        </p>
                                    </span></h3>

                                <ul class="mark_letter colorDeep qtDetail">
                                    <li tabindex="0">A. 对</li>
                                    <li tabindex="0">B. 错</li>
                                </ul>
                                <div class="mark_answer" tabindex="0">
                                    <div class="mark_key clearfix">
                                        <span class="colorDeep marginRight40 fl"><i
                                                class="fontWeight custom-style">我的答案:</i><span
                                                class="stuAnswerContent">错</span></span>
                                        <span class="colorGreen marginRight40 fl">
                                            <i class="fontWeight custom-style">正确答案:</i><span
